[I] A GNOME Web Browser and file navigator

[T] Epiphany is a fast and lightweight gtk+ Web Browser and File Navigator
[T] build around the Mozilla's Gecko rendering engine.
[T]
[T] The package seems to be a fork of galeon to rewrite it more cleanly
[T] and to conform to the GNOME human interface guidelines.

